import React from 'react' 

const Form = (props) => {
    return(
        <form onSubmit={props.handleFormSubmit} className="new-task-form">
            <input onChange={props.handleChange} type="text" placeholder="New task details"/>
            <select onChange={props.handleChange}> 
                <option>Food</option>
                <option>Money</option>
                <option>Code</option>
                <option>Misc</option>
            </select>
            <input type="submit" value="Add task"/>
        </form>
    )
}

export default Form
